=head1 DESCRIPTION

A wrapper structure for an X12 definition object.

the X12 envelope ensures the integrity of the data and the efficiency
of the information exchange. The X12 message structure has hierarchical
levels. From highest to the lowest, they are:

=over

=item *

Interchange Envelope

=item *

Functional Group

=item *

Transaction Set

=back


